{"tid":297900,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"F奶松嶋瑛美曲線100分　跑步胸部撞擊喊痛","createTime":"2017-06-25T23:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T11:50:09.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14e075fe9d92bd6e0c41eec898cb9693c007661f","tid":297900,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T23:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170625/420_f0e3a45e21cefa93176aab6c6585dfe0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170625%2F420_f0e3a45e21cefa93176aab6c6585dfe0.jpg&h=e044d1e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n松嶋瑛美擁有34F波霸上圍。彭欣偉攝<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170625/420_ee7cb4e14e49b9e4df8296994ba2ec17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170625%2F420_ee7cb4e14e49b9e4df8296994ba2ec17.jpg&h=b56b2852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n松嶋瑛美給自己的身材打了100分。彭欣偉攝<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170625/420_5dd8fd3c94612028c769e0fb9dd8a0ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170625%2F420_5dd8fd3c94612028c769e0fb9dd8a0ec.jpg&h=1a3ae886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n松嶋瑛美有8分之1的台灣血統。彭欣偉攝<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170625/420_e7baba264878deb03bd07c510bc6fa99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170625%2F420_e7baba264878deb03bd07c510bc6fa99.jpg&h=e758c8b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n松嶋瑛美雙腿修長，以誘人姿勢大秀性感魅力。彭欣偉攝<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170625/420_056a1a6359eeec97faacbf6d9cd2fd16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170625%2F420_056a1a6359eeec97faacbf6d9cd2fd16.jpg&h=96e422bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n松嶋瑛美第一次來台灣，特別以旗袍造型入鏡。彭欣偉攝<br />\n<br />\n25歲日本寫真女星松嶋瑛美日前首來台為日本美女寫真平台「@MISTY」上架站台，哈韓族的她自爆：「我超喜歡BIGBANG和他們的師弟團iKON，想更接近他們才決定出道，希望將來有機會和他們站在同一個舞台。」<br />\n<br />\n身材修長、擁有F罩杯波霸上圍的她，是8分之1的台日混血，外曾祖父是台灣人，這次首度來台還事前買了旅遊書做功課，不但如願逛了夜市，也大啖芒果冰消暑，讓她大呼過癮。<br />\n<br />\n她認為自己的身材有100分，但只給外型20分，因為自認長得不夠可愛，還透露上節目時被搞笑藝人形容為「醜女」，讓她很受傷，說：「粉絲認為我很可愛，就讓我很開心了。」<br />\n<br />\n她透露自己從小游泳、學過水上芭蕾，最近也開始練格鬥拳擊，笑說只要稍微運動，腹肌就會很明顯，因此不敢運動過頭。談到自己的傲人上圍，她認為胸大各有優缺點，說：「胸部大是寫真女星的優勢，缺點是沒辦法跑步，跑起來胸部晃來晃去會痛，也很難找到喜歡衣服款式的適合尺寸。」<br />\n<br />\n身高168公分的她，也自我調侃從沒碰過伸出鹹豬手的色狼，開玩笑表示：「我穿上高跟鞋，根本沒人敢靠過來吧？」松嶋瑛美坦言很欣賞模特兒女星菜菜緒，希望以她為努力目標。「@MISTY日本美女寫真館」網址：<a href=\"http://www.mistytw.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mistytw.com&d=cqr16t5r9tUJDj39CKmzKkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=cd26a83c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.mistytw.com</a>。（蘇威全／台北報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170625/1147319/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170625%2F1147319%2F&d=cqr16t5r9tUJDj39CKmzKkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=fc67096e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170625/1147319/</a>"},{"pid":"5c990080eeedea99d4cbf8f978e33cb8e406f16c","tid":297900,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"下海吧"},{"pid":"f2ba1e0f39c42c77e92142242e482ccf3711b910","tid":297900,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}